external_knowledge:
Active users are those with `is_active = 1`;
The date range '2023-01-01' AND '2023-12-31' corresponds to the entire year of 2023;
A user rating a movie more than once implies they have provided multiple ratings for the same movie, which are averaged to obtain the average rating.

sql:
SELECT movie_id
FROM favorite_movies
WHERE user_id = 0;

SELECT title
FROM movies
WHERE movie_id IN (
  SELECT movie_id
  FROM favorite_movies
);

SELECT COUNT(movie_id) AS favorite_count
FROM favorite_movies
WHERE user_id = 0;

SELECT COUNT(movie_id) AS comedy_movie_count
FROM movie_genre
WHERE genre_id = 1;

